        <definition>void report</definition>
        <argsstring>()</argsstring>
        <name>report</name>
        <briefdescription>
<para>Function to send a HW metrics message to data manager task. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para>The function request a pointer to the mailbox of data manager task and a message from message pool, set message type to eHwStatusAdxl37x, set <ref refid="struct_adxl37x" kindref="compound">Adxl37x</ref> task as sender, copy the HW metrics structure into payload of the message and send it to data manager&apos;s mailbox. </para>
        </detaileddescription>
