    <briefdescription>
<para><ref refid="class_hw_metrics" kindref="compound">HwMetrics</ref> class derived from task base class. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para><hruler/>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="par"><title>Detailed Description </title><para>The <ref refid="class_hw_metrics" kindref="compound">HwMetrics</ref> class is responsible to collect status informations from HW modules and to provide them to data manager. It provides a report method to send HW metrics data to data manager task and a method to translate incomming status information from <ref refid="struct_adxl37x" kindref="compound">Adxl37x</ref> task into HW metrics structure. <bold>Message Interaction:</bold><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Receive<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Power manager task</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="struct_adxl37x" kindref="compound">Adxl37x</ref> task</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Transmit<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Data manager task</para>
</listitem><listitem><para><ref refid="struct_adxl37x" kindref="compound">Adxl37x</ref> task </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
